- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses various training methods and optimization techniques. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving the performance of a machine translation system. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper focuses on neural networks and their optimization. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses optimizing the Transformer model on both GPU and CPU.
